# Pipeline Explanation

## Checkout
Pulls source code from GitHub repository.

## Build & Test
Uses Maven to compile and run unit tests.

## Dependency Scan
OWASP Dependency Check scans vulnerabilities in libraries.

## SonarQube
Performs static code analysis.

## Dockerfile Creation
Creates container definition dynamically.

## Kaniko Build
Builds container image without Docker daemon.

## Trivy Scan
Scans project for vulnerabilities.
